  "description": {
    "S": "Better than takeout! This crispy homemade Orange Peel Chicken features tender bite-sized chicken pieces coated in cornstarch and tossed in a glossy, sweet-tangy orange sauce with hints of garlic and sriracha heat. A delicious Asian-inspired dish that's surprisingly easy to make from scratch."
  },
